reviews.review_data: Reviewed in the United States on November 8, 2020
reviews.name: Tyler
reviews.title: Bundle Cost?
reviews.review: This Bundle is basically pointless and has a very noticeable lie on price. It says if purchased as a bundle you save $130. But if you go click on each product separately to price check, you notice you arent saving any money purchasing as a bundle. So just a heads up.
